Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 會議正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎各位出席商店街青年部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,廟會活動委員臨時集會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是今天的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,羽澤咖啡廳的羽澤鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來開始點名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,山吹麵包房的沙綾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,北澤肉鋪的育美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,青年部太鼓帶頭人巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和她的妹妹亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再為吾呈上暗黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,甘甜又氣泡充足的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一杯可樂是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你怎麼在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有商店街之處必有我摩卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她是山吹麵包房的常客了
Comment: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,OPZH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我們還迎來了一位新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,旭湯的朝日六花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我作為Galaxy的工作人員跟各位見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是受店長委託
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是還不是很清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們幾個也在慢慢摸索著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其實吧 是這次商店街要搞個活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到海報了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,「身心健康 Go Go」廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,健康Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我被商店街的老一輩們點了名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想招呼一批年輕人進來保持商店街的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小鶇 來弄一個Love什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就那個Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是和巴一起弄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,樂器的演奏會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你說演唱會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Live
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真懷念咱的青春時代啊 小米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱幾個也穿校服整了一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三味線的演奏會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好青春呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然後Afterglow就決定要出演了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說商店街的各個店鋪都會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello-Happy你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要弄可樂餅Live哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可樂餅Live？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,PopiPa的各位不出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起來肯定更開心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能去問一聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 雖然已經能猜到回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去！當然想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們主辦的演唱會那邊沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正在列場地的清單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那個廟會是每年都辦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我們家會擺攤賣麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有育美家的可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個可好吃了 含稅才86日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那會場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說會在戶外現搭一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 露天演唱會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,說了兩遍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第三遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相當重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就回覆她們說要參加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要和Afterglow一起演出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,還得決定曲目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,得開始練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起來拚命練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巴 節奏太趕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我太期待健康Go啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,巴你最喜歡廟會了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓那邊要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還用說嗎 當然也全力以赴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦 小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再不快點山吹麵包房就要關門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然要面對吃不上面包的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到活下去的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是在這裡搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,商店街的老一輩現在也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 她們好像還做了團扇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,燃起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,預備 一 二 哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為巴你也會配合的 好過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這部分就照往常來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,緋瑪麗好來勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,給各位獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是巧克力螺旋麵包好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟這是山吹麵包房的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆把店名加進歌詞裡弄成廣告一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想買麵包哪裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就去山吹麵包房～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,難得一場廟會 還是想盡興一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要唱Happy Happy Party？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定嗨得起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,曲目編排就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy已經同意給我們租器材了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們提前一天去搬出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好來勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為又要準備廟會 又想多練習一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太努力又累倒了可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦 那我會儘量不累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還是一如既往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,夕陽好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在國中的學園祭表演之後看到的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那畢竟是我們的第一場演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之後也看了好多次夕陽呢 我們五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 這不是LOCK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an7\1a&H30&\1cF5CAFF\blur2\bord0\pos(30,-80)}m 10 120 l 10 270 780 270 780 120
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fnDQKLDGSU}竟然！意想不到！Poppin'Party也決定參演！！\N{\b0\fs35}這是一支由（各位成員）組成的\N既可愛又讓人心動的樂團，真的非常可愛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party也決定參演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特地為我們貼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是咱們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party 即將開演！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是LOCK特地幫我們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,還想在這邊唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是最後一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就搬去舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 蔬菜店會用車幫我們運過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真期待明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要玩得盡興哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家風雨兼程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我宣布 第19屆身心健康 Go Go廟會 正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,請看可樂餅Live
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我買二十個！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因為廟會名字有Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:56.52,Tips,,0,0,0,,註：日語“五”與英文Go發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以五百日元Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第一首曲子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然下起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 那些設備！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只能再把它們搬回Galaxy了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫好卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,原定在廟會廣場進行的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因下雨暫時中止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再重複一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的話就用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 是羽澤咖啡廳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這雨會停嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣預報雖然說到了傍晚就會停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子都濕透了 興致全被澆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這是亞子送的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也把它分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 山吹麵包房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力螺旋麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你們已經習慣露天演唱會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你們都那麼冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也只能等著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事 都只是照常發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow是怎麼聚在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是回過神來就在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟都是一起長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小學還在同一個班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是國二的時候 只有蘭被分到了別的班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然後五個人就難得見一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,樂團…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來組樂團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想過怎麼讓我們五個人又能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以覺得大家一起辦一件事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會有很多時間聚起來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我覺得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好像好久沒看到蘭的這種表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Omnis 意思是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然聽著很帥 但總感覺不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,紫外線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還是取個有意義的名字比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟樂團叫紫外線的 還是太難懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要有我們風格的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,夕陽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們總是在放學之後練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是傍晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,翻譯成英語的話
Comment: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(Sunset,日落)？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}日落
Comment: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,(Evening,夜晚)？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這個名字覺得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,決定了 我們的樂團名字就叫Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們一直都在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,簡單說來就是難捨難分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟都經歷過那麼多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有的有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 咱還有個大目標對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,朝著武道館前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,武道館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還是像平常一樣在一起才最開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到了各位深厚的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雨小了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎停了 能不能再開演呢
